{"tid":1775660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(大搜查)藍絲暴徒針對記者行使暴力","createTime":"2019-12-09T03:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T03:58:16.000Z","uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4a9ac394a22feadcc167de0a1f76d5f0f57ea7","tid":1775660,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"【暴徒停手-壹週刊譴責聲明】<br />\n<br />\n本刊記者於12月9日早上，在黃大仙港鐵站拍攝「大三罷」行動期間，五名戴口罩男女疑是有組織而來的「藍絲」，將我們包圍並出手阻礙拍攝，當中有人企圖搶奪記者的攝錄器材，導致記者手腕受傷。<br />\n<br />\n本刊對於有暴徒針對記者行使暴力，並妨礙香港新聞自由，予以強烈譴責。本刊不容任何人以暴力干擾記者採訪，使香港蒙上暴力恐嚇陰影，也保留對暴徒的一切追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n壹週刊編輯部<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/4OBndFeHg2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2F4OBndFeHg2&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=21f3883b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/4OBndFeHg2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjofZzU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjofZzU.png&h=f4e31b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}